title: Analog Ambience - Atmospheric Synth & Electronic Music
description: A growing collection of modern and retro sounding minimalist tracks using analog synthesizers.
longDescription:
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mHFnIvJW8ZU&list=OLAK5uy_mWOSo4SeQbjALY5eUR7G_KtvMJXRqtRQA

Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/voltzsupreme/sets/analog-ambience-game-dev-music


An expanding collection of looping ambient and minimalist compositions performed by voltage architect and composer Voltz Supreme using mostly modern and vintage analog synthesizers.


From lo-fi to modern, this pack is currently being grown into a versatile library of tracks that will cater for a wide range of applications. Suggestions welcome via email.


Please credit "Music by Voltz Supreme" when using this music in your project.


- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 

Please rate or leave a review as this encourages me to provide you with more content via updates.
